acf.short_description:
Criniti’s is the best Italian restaurant in Parramatta, serving authentic Italian flavours in the Western Suburbs. Conveniently located at 328 Church St, Parramatta NSW 2150, our restaurant offers an ideal venue to celebrate with family and friends. Our menu features more than 300 items, including the best-woodfired pizzas, ribs, pasta, seafood, grilled fish, bruschetta, risotto, and more, combining Southern Italian and contemporary Australian cuisine.

At Criniti’s, we take pride in serving the freshest ingredients, cooked to perfection, and served with a smile. Whether you’re in the mood for a quick bite or a leisurely meal, our menu caters to all tastes and dietary requirements. From classic pizzas to hearty pasta dishes, you’ll find something you love at Criniti’s.

Don’t miss the opportunity to experience the best Italian restaurant in Parramatta. Visit us at Criniti’s Parramatta and indulge in the flavours of Italy. Make a reservation now at crinitis.com.au and check out our menu to explore our delicious offerings. You can also find us on Google Maps for directions to our location. (a few meters from Westfield Parramatta)

As the best Italian restaurant in Parramatta, we also offer an ideal event location for your function. Our famous 1mts, 2mts, and 3mts woodfired pizzas are prepared using our secret recipe dough and only the freshest ingredients. Our menu also features authentic Italian antipasti, ribs, steaks, burgers, gourmet salads, great cocktails, and an impressive selection of wines. And, of course, no meal at Criniti’s would be complete without one of our authentic Italian classic desserts.

The ambiance of our restaurant is perfect for any occasion, group bookings, or corporate events. Celebrating a birthday in Parramatta or Celebrating an event in Parramatta, don’t worry. Criniti’s got you covered. Head to our website, crinitis.com.au, or BOOK NOW to secure your party. At Criniti’s, our set menus cover a range of food plus dietary requirements plus unlimited refills* while you celebrate your event at Criniti’s Parramatta.

Parramatta is a bustling suburb that is perfect for those who like to be in the heart of the action. With plenty of shopping, dining, and entertainment options available, and not to forget this suburb is also home to many sporting clubs, including the Parramatta Eels rugby league team and the [Western Sydney Wanderers football team]. For a quick meal before the game or want to take away woodfired pizza, feel free to [Order Online] to pick up or schedule a pickup before the game. Criniti’s Parramatta is one of the late-night food restaurants to satisfy your Italian cravings. Secure a late-night spot on weekends.

BOOK NOW

So come and join us at Criniti’s Parramatta, where you’ll find the perfect spot to dine, relax, and enjoy the best Italian restaurant in Australia. With our delicious food and welcoming atmosphere.

page.post_content:
Welcome to Criniti's - the leading restaurant chain serving the best of Italian cuisine with a contemporary Australian twist. Our menu features mouth-watering wood-fired pizzas, pasta, seafood, grilled fish, bruschetta, risotto, ribs, and more. With multiple locations across the country, including Carlton, Southbank, Perth, Castle Hill, Parramatta (next to Bay Vista), Brighton Le Sand, Wetherill Park, and 5 more locations to come this year, we offer a unique dining experience at each of our locations.

At Criniti's, we use only the freshest ingredients and our secret dough recipe to bring you the best wood-fired pizzas in town. Whether you're looking for a quick bite or a leisurely meal, we have something for everyone. Our menu also includes authentic Italian antipasti, steaks, burgers, gourmet salads, cocktails, and an impressive wine selection.

Celebrate any occasion with family and friends at Criniti's - the perfect venue for your event. And don't forget to finish off your meal with one of our authentic Italian classic desserts. Come visit us at any of our locations and experience the taste of Italy right here in Australia.

Keep an eye out for new Criniti's locations coming soon!

This is why at Criniti's we say, when you're here, you're family...salute!
